There is so much variation in this game that you can't cover all possibilities of group makeup. In essense you should at least learn what all the class are capable of. Especially read through the spell lists. All kinds of tactics will jump out at you. <br>
The problem is the game changes alot 50+. Many high level mobs require fairly specific tactics. Many mobs are resistant to all but a very few spells if not totally resistant. <br>
Many times you will have to fail in order to learn how to succeed. Just try to fail in a spot where you can get your corpse. <br>
